title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Pitchfork of Seltzers
description:
Throwing Fits has officially joined a previous podcast endeavor that shall not be named in the 1 million downloads club so The Only Podcast That Matters™ is celebrating the only way we know how, with another thousand dollar dinner. Until then, it’s pure, raw, uncut gloating for The Core 4 and our best friends behind the paywall as we discuss boys night eve butterflies, pandemic podcasting lines of demarcation, being the influencers we wish to see in the world, flow team politics and much more. Three cheers for the Throw Gang!
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
